# Kademic Platform

Kademic is an online class management platform that helps students with assignments, discussion posts, and full online course support.

## Features

- Assignment help ($15 per page)
- Discussion posts ($7)
- Full class management (5-week and 8-week options)
- Referral system ($100 credit per referral)

## Tech Stack

- Frontend: React + Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Node.js + Express
- Database: MongoDB

## Project Status

🚧 Currently in development (30-day build challenge)